data.description: Come and experience this beautiful 4 Bedroom and 2.5 Bath home, in Virginia Beach's sought-after Castleton neighborhood!! The home offers a beautiful master suite with a bonus sitting area, oversized vanity, walk-in closet, step-in shower with separate soaking tub! Spacious eat-in kitchen with separate formal dining room! Large open floor concept and beautiful LVP flooring flows throughout the downstairs living area with tile flooring in the kitchen! Enjoy peace and serenity on your large deck as the back of the home is nestled on the lake! Save on your power bills with the solar panels that convey and have already been paid off for you! New sprinkler system installed in 2022, roof replaced in 2019! Minutes from NAS Oceana/Damn Neck bases, shopping and beaches! Located in the Highly Sought After Strawbridge Elementary School District!
